# Edges and Specialization

As adventurers grow in power, they develop unique capabilities that set them apart from others of similar training. These edges represent specialized techniques, natural talents, and hard-won expertise—the small choices that define who you are as a hero.

## What Are Edges?

At each minor milestone (typically every 1-2 sessions), you may choose to take an edge instead of advancing a skill or attribute. While skills and attributes measure broad capability, edges represent focused specialization in narrow areas.

Some edges can also be earned through play without spending milestones—social connections, languages, and unique story rewards can emerge naturally from your adventures.

