### Skill Specialization

Rather than improving your skill across all situations, you can instead gain +1 to a specific application of that skill. This represents the kind of focused expertise that comes from repeated experience in particular circumstances.

Unlike most edges, you can take Skill Specialization multiple times as long as each application is different. A character might specialize in Urban Stealth, Combat Dueling, and Empathy for Reading Lies—each a distinct narrow use of a broader skill.

